List out names of tables available from OxCOVID19 Database

Source: R/utilities.R
list_tables.Rd

List out names of tables available from OxCOVID19 Database

list_tables(con = connect_oxcovid19())

Arguments

con

A PqConnection class object specifying the PostgreSQL connection to OxCOVID19 Database. This is produced by connect_covid19 function

Value

A vector of table names available from OxCOVID19 Database

Examples

list_tables()
#>  [1] "weather"                 "world_bank"             
#>  [3] "mobility"                "epidemiology"           
#>  [5] "government_response"     "world_bank_time_series" 
#>  [7] "diagnostics"             "baseline_mortality"     
#>  [9] "administrative_division" "spatial_ref_sys"        
#> [11] "geography_columns"       "geometry_columns"       
#> [13] "country_statistics"
